Standards-Version: 3.9.0
Section: libs
Homepage: http://www.directfb.org/

Package: libdirectfb-1.5
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, linux-fusion-dkms,
 libdirectfb-1.5-wm, libdirectfb-1.5-system
Recommends: libdirectfb-1.5-imageprovider-gif, libdirectfb-1.5-imageprovider-png,
 libdirectfb-1.5-imageprovider-jpeg, libdirectfb-1.5-fontprovider-dgiff,
 libdirectfb-1.5-fontprovider-ft2, libdirectfb-1.5-wm-default
Description: DirectFB - shared libraries
 DirectFB is a graphics library which was designed with embedded systems
 in mind. It offers maximum hardware accelerated performance at a minimum
 of resource usage and overhead.

